'''闊葉樹'''是對[[被子植物|被子植物]]中所有[[树|树]]的統稱。一般闊葉樹的叶子是平的，並且闊葉樹的[[果实|果实]]内能结出[[种子|种子]]。它是两种常見的树木之一，另一种是[[针叶树|针叶树]]，這種樹木具有针状或鳞片状的叶子<ref>[http://oregonstate.edu/trees/dichotomous_key/ Dichotomous Key.] Common Trees of the Pacific Northwest. College of Forestry, Oregon State University.</ref>。大多数[[落葉樹|落叶树]]屬於阔叶树<ref name=":0">Lee, S. and A. Raflo. [http://www.vwrrc.vt.edu/Treeswater/Part1.html Trees and Water.] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921154303/http://www.vwrrc.vt.edu/Treeswater/Part1.html|date=2016-09-21}} Virginia Water Resources Research Center. Virginia Tech.</ref>。

